1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,475
Turn your Switch into a D L N A media receiver.

2
00:00:03,425 --> 00:00:09,409
Launch N X Cast, select it as the playback device on your phone, and your video starts playing on the Switch.

3
00:00:09,409 --> 00:00:14,513
Control playback remotely from the phone, or use the touchscreen and controllers directly.

4
00:00:14,513 --> 00:00:19,398
N X Cast is open source, experimental, and continuously improving.

